  <brief_title>Comparison of Static Air Support Devices (Repose®) and Alternating-Pressure Devices in the Prevention of Pressure Ulcers</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pressure Ulcer Prevention Using Static Air Support Devices (Repose®) Versus Alternating-Pressure Devices in a High Risk Population in Nursing Homes: A Multi-Center Prospective Randomized Controlled Trial and Qualitative Study</official_title>
